title: Darkchylde Vol. 1 (2011) (TPB) (Digital) (Minutemen-The Undead)
description:
Darkchylde Vol. 1: Legacy and Redemption

English | CBR | 1 Issue

Genre: Fantasy, Horror

Written by Randy Queen
Art by Sarah Queen, Ron Adrian and Randy Queen

Ariel Chylde, the girl who can become the creatures from her many nightmares, seeks salvation and a cure for her curse following the deadly events in Salem! Collected for the first time comes the fan favorite 'Legacy' and 'Redemption' storylines, with brand new art, and cover gallery by RANDY QUEEN.
